text: Ian Otieno (born 9 August 1993) is a Kenyan international footballer who plays for Red Arrows, as a Goalkeeper. ==Career== Born in Siaya, Otieno has played club football for Posta Rangers, A.F.C. Leopards and Red Arrows. He made his international debut for Kenya in 2015. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Kenyan footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Posta Rangers F.C. players Category:A.F.C.
